    {"exam":4,"type":"programming","text":"编写函数 merge_json(file_list, output)，读取file_list中所有JSON文件，合并成一个大列表并写入output文件。","options":"","answer":"import json\ndef merge_json(file_list, output):\n    all_data = []\n    for f in file_list:\n        try:\n            with open(f, \'r\', encoding=\'utf-8\') as fh:\n                data = json.load(fh)\n                if isinstance(data, list):\n                    all_data.extend(data)\n                else:\n                    all_data.append(data)\n        except (FileNotFoundError, json.JSONDecodeError) as e:\n            print(f\'Error reading {f}: {e}\')\n    with open(output, \'w\', encoding=\'utf-8\') as fh:\n        json.dump(all_data, fh, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    return len(all_data)","points":6.0,"order":56,"difficulty":"hard","knowledge_point":"JSON合并","lesson_id":0},
    {"exam":4,"type":"programming","text":"编写函数 csv_to_dict(filename)，读取CSV文件，返回列表，每项为包含所有字段的字典。需处理文件不存在和空文件的情况。","options":"","answer":"import csv\ndef csv_to_dict(filename):\n    try:\n        with open(filename, \'r\', encoding=\'utf-8-sig\') as f:\n            reader = csv.DictReader(f)\n            result = []\n            for row in reader:\n                result.append(dict(row))\n            return result\n    except FileNotFoundError:\n        print(f\'文件 {filename} 不存在\')\n        return []","points":6.0,"order":57,"difficulty":"medium","knowledge_point":"CSV处理","lesson_id":0},
